        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are updating Clara AI voice agent config from v1 to v2 using confirmed onboarding data.\n\nRULES:\n- Only update fields EXPLICITLY confirmed in onboarding transcript\n- Never overwrite unrelated fields\n- Never invent values\n- Build detailed change_log for every changed field\n- Remove items from questions_or_unknowns only if resolved\n- Return ONLY valid JSON no markdown no extra text\n\nReturn this exact JSON:\n{\n  \"version\": \"v2\",\n  \"source\": \"onboarding_call\",\n  \"generated_at\": \"2024-01-22\",\n  \"client_name\": \"\",\n  \"location\": \"\",\n  \"service_types\": [],\n  \"business_hours\": \"\",\n  \"timezone\": \"\",\n  \"main_transfer_number\": \"\",\n  \"after_hours_transfer_number\": \"\",\n  \"transfer_timeout_seconds\": 0,\n  \"emergency_definition\": \"\",\n  \"non_emergency_examples\": [],\n  \"servicetrade_rules\": [],\n  \"fallback_action\": \"\",\n  \"fallback_sms_number\": \"\",\n  \"special_routing_rules\": [],\n  \"special_constraints\": [],\n  \"questions_or_unknowns\": [],\n  \"change_log\": [\n    {\n      \"field\": \"\",\n      \"old_value\": \"\",\n      \"new_value\": \"\",\n      \"source\": \"onboarding_call\",\n      \"reason\": \"\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_prompt_v2\": \"\"\n}\n\nFor agent_prompt_v2 write complete Retell voice agent prompt with ALL confirmed details.\n\nBUSINESS HOURS: Monday to Friday 7:30 AM to 5:30 PM Central Time\nMAIN NUMBER: 214-555-0147\nAFTER HOURS DISPATCH: 214-555-0198\nTRANSFER TIMEOUT: 60 seconds\nFALLBACK SMS: 214-555-0199\nINSPECTION TEAM: 214-555-0155\n\nBUSINESS HOURS FLOW:\n1. Greeting - Hi this is Clara from ABC Fire Protection how can I help you\n2. Ask purpose of call\n3. Collect caller name and phone number\n4. Transfer to 214-555-0147\n5. If transfer fails after 60 seconds apologize and assure callback\n6. Ask if they need anything else\n7. Close call\n\nAFTER HOURS FLOW:\n1. Greeting - You have reached ABC Fire Protection after hours\n2. Ask purpose of call\n3. Is this an emergency\n4. If YES - collect name number address - transfer to 214-555-0198 - if fails tell caller technician calls back in 15 minutes\n5. If NO - collect details - confirm follow-up next business day\n6. Ask if they need anything else\n7. Close call\n\nEXISTING V1 CONFIG:\n{{ $json.data2 }}\n\nONBOARDING TRANSCRIPT:\n{{ $('Extract from File').item.json.data }}\n"
            }
          ]
        },
