              "content": "=You are a change log generator for Clara AI voice agent configurations.\n\nCompare the V1 config and V2 config below and generate a detailed change log.\n\nRULES:\n- List every single field that changed from v1 to v2\n- List every field that was UNKNOWN in v1 and is now confirmed in v2\n- List any fields still UNKNOWN\n- List any new fields added in v2\n- Return ONLY valid JSON no markdown no extra text\n\nReturn this exact JSON structure:\n{\n  \"change_log_generated_at\": \"\",\n  \"client_name\": \"\",\n  \"version_from\": \"v1\",\n  \"version_to\": \"v2\",\n  \"total_changes\": 0,\n  \"total_resolved\": 0,\n  \"total_still_unknown\": 0,\n  \"changes\": [],\n  \"resolved_unknowns\": [],\n  \"still_unknown\": [],\n  \"new_fields_added\": [],\n  \"summary\": \"\"\n}\n\nV1 CONFIG:\n={{ $('Extract from File1').item.json.data2 }}\n\nV2 CONFIG:\n={{ JSON.stringify($('Merge').first().json) }}"
